                </quote>;</text>
						</clause>
          </subparagraph>
          <subparagraph commented="no" id="HEDA3A8156C3B467E99F67F7A2E41E2FA">
            <enum>(D)</enum>
            <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="STOCK Act/s:8/ss:b/p:3">paragraph (3)</cato:entity-ref>,
