              <text>by
			 amending <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="STOCK Act/s:11/ss:b/p:1/sp:B">subparagraph (B)</cato:entity-ref> to read as follows:</text>
